{"tid":1630550,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唯有人權法先能懲罰狗隻狗官,請不要失焦","createTime":"2019-10-06T12:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T13:07:52.000Z","uid":3508,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dde3512447b0348e368dde044b622ae76f1aee71","tid":1630550,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:52:12.000Z","msg":"裝修只能夠一時發洩,果一刻係好爽<br />\n但班狗官,狗隻WFC,完全唔關佢地事,影響佢地唔到<br />\n依家要做既反而係理性勇武<br />\n我地唔係怕左蒙面法<br />\n要蒙面,日常做就可以<br />\n依家反而唔好中計令國際以為香港真係變左好多真暴徒既地方,出緊急法制亂係應該<br />\n呢幾日狗隻乜都唔做就係想你地破壞<br />\n等政府有口實去支持令風向改變<br />\n唔好令國際社會風向轉變<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">反而應該加強文宣,宣傳係支共派黑社會出黎破壞再嫁禍義士,目的係佢地慣常既分化手段</span></span><br />\n只要人權法一過<br />\n班狗官命運自然會黎<br />\n到時睇下邊個笑到最後<br />\n唔好因為一時爽快<br />\n俾復仇感搞到失去理性<br />\n我地依家係要打長期戰<br />\n一時爽快幫唔到大局<br />\n反而人權法同國際支持先係正道<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不割蓆,但要理性,為大局著想</span></span>"},{"pid":"137d0b4726c00ce321f567d20c82990f5aff410b","tid":1630550,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"d7470406349fa8deb092f8481670153420b0cb30","tid":1630550,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:53:28.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"0762484395fad411c9d7881daf60251e5fc4b765","tid":1630550,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:53:46.000Z","msg":"推3"},{"pid":"f07078e659a70c92ef4738bacbe779496ed96d06","tid":1630550,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:54:33.000Z","msg":"推4"},{"pid":"90633a523e0ffa4f53f58001f308da09566c2864","tid":1630550,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"推5"},{"pid":"90914d6e39e63e673a6e63fd71d782afcc3cf22f","tid":1630550,"uid":249794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:55:31.000Z","msg":"[長文][召喚全世界] 嘈完就入黎 睇下下一步應該做咩<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630553\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630553</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84c37e925950127b7cf81d172925753a23c35b35","tid":1630550,"uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:55:48.000Z","msg":"dllm <br />\n幫手report<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tfwXea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tfwXea.png&h=49b8c28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ParliamentHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FParliamentHK&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6ubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=3dac8215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ParliamentHK</a><br />\n<br />\n因為個宣言第一段有中共味道呀<br />\n中777同習圈套呀<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9PA5heU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9PA5heU.png&h=1fd0514f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ef4a8b5b716a38e13539de36f49dccbc5588600","tid":1630550,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"一定要靠美國<br />\n以後行動應該係要增取美國更多支持"},{"pid":"67647a5d38f67078ffe06c492330c41e0acbd9b3","tid":1630550,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:56:49.000Z","msg":"推6"},{"pid":"8b43940c497793ded7877d16e14c2142ad1beb12","tid":1630550,"uid":82699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:56:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />push"},{"pid":"fb5e3ed258c24e2b0fd7c9905a58225944a91e15","tid":1630550,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:58:18.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"6050bfb7879c650542b0b1209af95f35430ba988","tid":1630550,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:58:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aad6578fd7104f8f040841cfe785db91df087686","tid":1630550,"uid":178440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f44b805f64aec84391cef309422d8bc01b1a1eeb","tid":1630550,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:01:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60fa1351d3b613cbee18580d4692645777137649","tid":1630550,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"277493c6eb79ae266906f72be2d738be45475b2f","tid":1630550,"uid":283668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:06:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兄弟！一齊拆！</span></span><br />\n因為個宣言第一段有中共味道呀<br />\n中777同習圈套呀<br />\n<br />\n幫手report<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0tfwXea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0tfwXea.png&h=49b8c28a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ParliamentHK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FParliamentHK&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6ubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=3dac8215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ParliamentHK</a><br />\n<br />\n對家已起底，見一個report 一個<br />\n見圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcqdrbw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmcqdrbw.jpg&h=a4feb115&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：共產黨玩嘢，香港人領嘢。咁都領嘢？枉為香港人。香港人不聽陳雲的話，犯上政治錯誤，犧牲幾多人都是被共產黨收割，之後糟蹋。<br />\n如果你識字，就知道第一句是共產黨的意識形態。破舊立新，而且強調歷史發展的必然性。<br />\n香港人昨晚十八區，宣讀共產主義宣言，而且宣言隻字不提美國為香港人權立法監護香港的貢獻，美國的有識之士被香港人激死了。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157462752772225?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10157462752772225%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6ubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=03a3ab13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10157462752772225?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同時有香港獨立黨出聲明攻擊香港人權及民主法、又有臨時議會成立、又有臨時政府成立、又有連登「我有個讀政治的朋友」寫了香港憲法？同時又有練乙燈出文再提港獨？全部舉動幾日內急急推出，全部都是指向推翻美國「人權及民主法」的保障香港自治的立法前設？全部都是港共用了緊急法之後才忽然出現？<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100002094159071/posts/2498430470236734?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100002094159071%2Fposts%2F2498430470236734%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6ubr9%2BGymSeLOXabm6KdyvY%3D&h=eca2033c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100002094159071/posts/2498430470236734?sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"a30b21ab41eb4e0128ab19c6c9d0ba7446f8036e","tid":1630550,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:06:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請前線既手足記住幾點:<br />\n1. 目標要清晰, 唔能夠無差別攻擊, 見到有無差別帶頭請阻止。<span style=\"color: red;\">你地唔係野獸，你地出得去都係為左心中既理念，係針對政權。</span><br />\n<br />\n2. 裝修既野請跟住黑紅藍黃既準則. 唔能夠為發洩而破壞<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>, 記住發洩要發岩對象。發唔岩對象係冇作用。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n3. <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">請唔好變到好似大陸人咁玻璃心</span></strong>, 小小野就要喊打喊殺, 記住, 把口係人地度, 只係出口既話係唔會痛, <span style=\"color: red;\">正如政府一樣, 我地和理非講幾多佢都唔會理, 只會冷處理</span>. <span style=\"color: gold;\">但通常挑釁既人都會忍唔住出手先, 咁先有理由召喚神獸。</span><br />\n<br />\n請和理非既手足都記住幾點：<br />\n１.前線勇武既手足真係付出左好多, 我地要堅持<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">不分化, 不割蓆。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n2. 自己係連登都睇清楚POST同內容, 唔好俾人帶到風向, <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>依家連登好多時都有正反兩極既POST有好多, 目的就係要令到和勇兩邊無所適從, 自我分化</strong></span>. 但呢樣唔重要,<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 最重要既係, 對準政權, 對準保皇狗, 極紅資本及持槍恐怖分子。只要做既野對呢Ｄ有傷害就值得做。</span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"1cfd5fa052321fcbac185415ac45b339b151c1bf","tid":1630550,"uid":3508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}